title: Fiona Harper -Invitation to the Boss's Ball
description:
Invitation to the Boss's Ball 
by Fiona Harper 


An invitation to the ball...Alice's plain-Jane world is turned upside down when she's hired to organize tycoon Cameron Hunter's company ball....makes her feel like a princessShe's shocked by an invitation on her doormat, and the next thing she knows, she's dancing in her oh-so-delicious boss's arms in a stunning dress!...until the clock strikes midnight!
Alice knows that on Monday morning everything will go back to normal. But for now, she's going to enjoy every second
